snippet.title: Nuvoloso - Color Match Gameplay
snippet.description:
Nuvoloso is a free Arcade game for Android all about looking at clouds and finding ones in a specific shape. Play through a number of different gamemodes to unlock new powers and beat your highscore. You can also play against a friend in the local multiplayer VS mode to see who can get more clouds.

Download the game:
Google Play Store: https://play.google.com/store/apps/de...
Itch.io: https://cloudyo.itch.io/nuvoloso
Gamejolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/nuvoloso/416714

Music:
"Team Spirit" from http://www.freesfx.co.uk
